instructions:

Setup

1)  unzip into a non root dir
2)  run xampp/setup_xampp.bat
3)  run xampp/xampp-control.exe
4)  http://localhost can access mysqlphp
5)  copy site into xampp/htdocs/WB
6)  change myphp to english on the main screen
7)  create database michelde_wonderboy (defaults)
8)  create user for database michelde_wboy pwd Wonderboy with default prvi
9)  for the database, import the schema
10) change display_errors = Off in php.ini
11) new:  error_reporting=E_ALL & ~E_DEPRECATED & ~E_STRICT & ~E_NOTICE  (add the ~E_NOTICE to remove notices).

reload database

1)  Delete all tables using phpmysqladmin (from http://localhost)
2)  delete the views
3)  export and download the latest schema from internet and then import locally
